1b:[["$","span",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"Product overview"}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"What Are Pure Marine Collagen Capsules?"}],[["$","p","Are you looking to find a natural way to give your ageing skin a bit of a lift? Collagen has become the new talk of the town in the world of skincare, and it might just be exactly what you need!",{"children":"Are you looking to find a natural way to give your ageing skin a bit of a lift? Collagen has become the new talk of the town in the world of skincare, and it might just be exactly what you need!"}],["$","p","Our Pure Marine Collagen Capsules are specially designed to support your body's natural beauty from within. They’re packed with hydrolysed Type 1 and Type 3 collagen, the two key types found naturally in your skin, bones, and joints. Thanks to their hydrolysed form, they’re easier for your body to absorb , helping you get the most from every dose.",{"children":"Our Pure Marine Collagen Capsules are specially designed to support your body's natural beauty from within. They’re packed with hydrolysed Type 1 and Type 3 collagen, the two key types found naturally in your skin, bones, and joints. Thanks to their hydrolysed form, they’re easier for your body to absorb , helping you get the most from every dose."}],["$","p","Each serving delivers a powerful 1200mg of premium fish collagen peptides, making it a strong and simple way to top up your body’s collagen levels. Feel the benefit of collagen from the inside out with our Marine Collagen Capsules today!",{"children":"Each serving delivers a powerful 1200mg of premium fish collagen peptides, making it a strong and simple way to top up your body’s collagen levels. Feel the benefit of collagen from the inside out with our Marine Collagen Capsules today!"}],["$","p","Let your body harness the collagen glow with our Pure Marine Collagen Capsules.",{"children":"Let your body harness the collagen glow with our Pure Marine Collagen Capsules."}]]]
1c:["$","div",null,{"className":"productAccordions","children":[[["$","details","Benefits Of Pure Marine Collagen Capsules",{"className":"productAccordion","open":true,"children":[["$","summary",null,{"children":"Benefits Of Pure Marine Collagen Capsules"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"accordionBody","children":[[["$","p","Did you know that collagen makes up nearly 30% of all the proteins in your body? It plays a vital role in building connective tissue in various body parts, from your skin and joints to your bones and muscles. But as the years roll on, our natural collagen production starts to slow down, which manifests as signs of premature ageing, joint aches, weak bones and thinning hair.",{"children":"Did you know that collagen makes up nearly 30% of all the proteins in your body? It plays a vital role in building connective tissue in various body parts, from your skin and joints to your bones and muscles. But as the years roll on, our natural collagen production starts to slow down, which manifests as signs of premature ageing, joint aches, weak bones and thinning hair."}]],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li","That’s where Pure Marine Collagen Capsules step in. Here's how our Pure Marine Collagen Capsules impact you:",{"children":"That’s where Pure Marine Collagen Capsules step in. Here's how our Pure Marine Collagen Capsules impact you:"}],["$","li","Naturally helps replenish your collagen levels",{"children":"Naturally helps replenish your collagen levels"}],["$","li","Designed for taking care of your skin, bones, joints and muscles",{"children":"Designed for taking care of your skin, bones, joints and muscles"}],["$","li","Essential for maintaining your hair as collagen is found in the hair scalp",{"children":"Essential for maintaining your hair as collagen is found in the hair scalp"}],["$","li","Provides hydrolysed collagen peptides for easier absorption and impactful results",{"children":"Provides hydrolysed collagen peptides for easier absorption and